content:
We redesigned the data mapper page to enhance the visual sequence of your survey data maps. This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Feedback Management - Starter or Feedback Management - Growth is enabled.

SEE ALSO

title: Enhanced Data Mapper Page for Salesforce Feedback Management
